/* ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
   ML ‚Äî RF SIMULATION (mirrors your Python backend)
‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê */
const SIT_COLOR={low:"#22c55e",normal:"#eab308",heavy:"#f97316",high:"#ef4444"};
const SIT_SCORE={low:18,normal:42,heavy:68,high:88};

function rfPredict({hour,cars,bikes,buses,trucks}){
  const total=cars+bikes+buses+trucks;
  const peak=(hour>=7&&hour<=9)||(hour>=16&&hour<=19)?1:0;
  const tbr=(trucks+buses)/(total+1);
  let s=(total/180)*52+peak*26+tbr*14+(Math.random()*8-4);
  s=Math.max(5,Math.min(97,Math.round(s)));
  const sit=s<30?"low":s<55?"normal":s<75?"heavy":"high";
  return{score:s,sit,color:SIT_COLOR[sit],speed:Math.round(Math.max(8,65-s*0.57)),delay:Math.round(s/3.4),conf:Math.round(88+Math.random()*9),total};
}

function scoreFromHour(hour){
  const row=REAL_HOURLY[hour]||REAL_HOURLY[8];
  return Math.round((row.total/180)*78);
}

function buildLiveEdges(hour){
  return EDGES.map(e=>{
    const base=scoreFromHour(hour);
    const sc=Math.max(5,Math.min(97,base+Math.round((Math.random()-.5)*24)));
    const col=sc<30?"#22c55e":sc<55?"#eab308":sc<75?"#f97316":"#ef4444";
    const spd=Math.round(Math.max(8,e.speedLimit-(sc/100)*(e.speedLimit-8)));
    return{...e,score:sc,color:col,speed:spd,delay:Math.round(sc/3.4)};
  });
}

/* ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
   DIJKSTRA ‚Äî Shortest Path weighted by travel time
‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê */
function dijkstra(liveEdges,start,end){
  const graph={};
  liveEdges.forEach(e=>{
    if(!graph[e.from])graph[e.from]=[];
    if(!graph[e.to])  graph[e.to]=[];
    const tt=(e.km/Math.max(5,e.speed))*60;// minutes
    graph[e.from].push({node:e.to,  cost:tt,km:e.km,score:e.score,color:e.color,name:e.name,speed:e.speed});
    graph[e.to].push(  {node:e.from,cost:tt,km:e.km,score:e.score,color:e.color,name:e.name,speed:e.speed});
  });
  const dist={},prev={},vis=new Set();
  Object.keys(LOCATIONS).forEach(n=>dist[n]=Infinity);
  dist[start]=0;
  const pq=[[0,start]];
  while(pq.length){
    pq.sort((a,b)=>a[0]-b[0]);
    const[d,u]=pq.shift();
    if(vis.has(u))continue;vis.add(u);
    if(u===end)break;
    (graph[u]||[]).forEach(({node,cost,km,score,color,name,speed})=>{
      const nd=d+cost;
      if(nd<dist[node]){dist[node]=nd;prev[node]={from:u,cost,km,score,color,name,speed};pq.push([nd,node]);}
    });
  }
  const path=[];let cur=end;
  while(cur){path.unshift(cur);cur=prev[cur]?.from;}
  const segs=path.slice(1).map((n,i)=>({from:path[i],to:n,...prev[n]}));
  const totalKm=segs.reduce((a,s)=>a+(s.km||0),0);
  return{path,segs,totalTime:Math.round(dist[end]||0),totalKm:Math.round(totalKm*10)/10};
}

/* ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
   LEAFLET MAP ‚Äî FREE, NO API KEY, REAL OPENSTREETMAP + CARTO DARK
‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê */
function LeafletMap({liveEdges,route,origin,dest,onMarkerClick}){
  const containerRef=useRef(null);
  const mapRef=useRef(null);
  const layersRef=useRef([]);

  function initMap(){
    if(!containerRef.current||mapRef.current)return;
    const L=window.L;
    mapRef.current=L.map(containerRef.current,{center:[17.406,78.477],zoom:12,zoomControl:true});
    L.tileLayer("https://{s}.basemaps.cartocdn.com/dark_all/{z}/{x}/{y}{r}.png",{
      attribution:'¬© <a href="https://www.openstreetmap.org/">OSM</a> ¬© <a href="https://carto.com/">CARTO</a>',
      subdomains:"abcd",maxZoom:19
    }).addTo(mapRef.current);
    redraw();
  }

  function clearLayers(){
    layersRef.current.forEach(l=>{try{mapRef.current.removeLayer(l);}catch(e){}});
    layersRef.current=[];
  }

  function redraw(){
    if(!mapRef.current||!window.L)return;
    clearLayers();
    const L=window.L;
    const routeSet=new Set((route?.segs||[]).flatMap(s=>[`${s.from}-${s.to}`,`${s.to}-${s.from}`]));

    liveEdges.forEach(e=>{
      const A=LOCATIONS[e.from],B=LOCATIONS[e.to];
      if(!A||!B)return;
      const isR=routeSet.has(`${e.from}-${e.to}`);
      if(isR){
        const glow=L.polyline([[A.lat,A.lng],[B.lat,B.lng]],{color:"#3b82f6",weight:20,opacity:.12}).addTo(mapRef.current);
        layersRef.current.push(glow);
      }
      const line=L.polyline([[A.lat,A.lng],[B.lat,B.lng]],{
        color:isR?"#60a5fa":e.color,weight:isR?7:4,opacity:isR?1:.72,dashArray:isR?"14,7":null,
      }).addTo(mapRef.current);
      line.bindPopup(
        `<div style="background:#0a1628;color:#e2e8f0;padding:14px;border-radius:10px;font-family:sans-serif;min-width:210px">
          <div style="font-size:9px;color:#5a7098;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px">${isR?"‚ú¶ SHORTEST PATH SEGMENT":"ROAD SEGMENT"}</div>
          <div style="font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px">${e.name}</div>
          <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px">
            <div style="background:#060f1e;border-radius:6px;padding:8px;text-align:center">
              <div style="font-size:9px;color:#5a7098">CONGESTION</div>
